query: SELECT sourceLanguage, targetLanguage, city, state, COUNT(*) as count FROM interpreters WHERE sourceLanguage LIKE '%-%' OR sourceLanguage LIKE '% -%' OR targetLanguage LIKE '%-%' OR LENGTH(sourceLanguage) > 50 GROUP BY sourceLanguage, targetLanguage, city, state ORDER BY count DESC LIMIT 20;
